snippet.title: Reverse Speech - Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Defamation Lawsuit
snippet.description:
This channel is not monetized, but donations are gratefully accepted:
http://www.paypal.me/rsanalyst.

Reverse Speech is a phenomenon of the unconscious mind which can be heard when the human voice is played in reverse. The unconscious mind is hard wired to tell the truth, so Reverse Speech can reveal a person's inner thoughts and feelings even when the person is not being honest in normal forward speech.  See www.reversespeech.com for info on classes, products, and thousands of speech reversals!

Reverse Speech offers us unusual insights into human psychology and is helpful in understanding criminal behavior.

Questions on Reverse Speech may be sent to reversespeak@gmail.com.
